result.title: Question about open cup
result.content:
I participated GP of Ukraine with my ID : seoulnu07 (Although I participated as ACGTeam until the last competition, our team lost on the icpc regional contest and the team is provisionally disbanded :( ).

Until ~2hr, There was my team on yandex scoreboard, but submissions after 2hr did not apply to the scoreboard. I got 9 problems, but the scoreboard said that seoulnu07 solved 6 problems. Also, I could't find my team in the official scoreboard.

There was no problem when I participated as ACGTeam, so is it a problem about multiple IDs? How to fix this problem?
